              <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="europe"></a>Understanding the European Union. Wednesday 1st June, 8pm at All Saints Church Hall</h3>
              <p>Finding the referendum confusing?  Wonder what is fact and what is fancy?  All welcome to a meeting with Rev Jeremy Groombridge, former senior civil servant who has a lot of experience of working with the European Commission.</p>
              </td>
              <td class="events">
